| Feature | Legacy Welfare | Civic Care Unit (CCU) |
|---------|----------------|----------------------|
| Middlemen | High (Ministries/NGOs) | Zero (Direct Smart Contracts) |
| Speed | Months (Bureaucracy) | Hours (Trigger-based) |
| Data Ownership | Owned by State | Owned by Citizen (Encrypted) |
| Audit Frequency | Yearly/Internal | Real-time/Public Ledger |
| Political Gain | High (Buying votes) | Negative (System is "Politician-Proof") |
| Fraud Rate | 15-30% | Target <2% |
| Administrative Overhead | 40-60% of budget | Target <10% of budget |
| User Satisfaction | 30-40% | Target >80% |
| Appeal Process | Opaque, slow | Transparent, 72-hour response |
| Technology Access | Assumes digital literacy | Multi-modal (app, card, kiosk, proxy) |

